<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is an insider trading hypothetical that I=
 have never considered before. You are a talented business executive with a=
 high profile. A public company has publicly announced that its chief execu=
tive officer is leaving and that it is looking for a replacement.<a class=
=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-3" style=3D"color: #000000; text-deco=
ration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00=
0000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transparent !=
important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[3]</span>
</a>=C2=A0You think you=E2=80=99d be perfect for the job. The company calls=
 you in for an interview. The interview goes well. =E2=80=9CWe=E2=80=99ll l=
et you know in a few weeks,=E2=80=9D they say, but you have a joint good fe=
eling that:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">they will give you the job and</li>=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">you will be good at it.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So you go buy some shares of the company=E2=80=
=99s stock, as a bet that (1) they=E2=80=99ll hire you as CEO and (2) the s=
tock will go up as the market realizes how good you are at the job.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Is that insider trading? I mean, I guess. You =
have some=C2=A0nonpublic information (you were in the interview and know it=
 went well), and that information is probably material to the average share=
holder (having a CEO in place is probably good for the stock, and if you ar=
e a high-profile person maybe your name will move the stock). The nonpublic=
 information is not purely about your own intentions.=C2=A0Still there is s=
omething a bit soft about it. You=E2=80=99re not betting that the stock wil=
l go up because you have secret information about earnings or a merger. You=
=E2=80=99re betting that the stock will go up because you will turn out to =
be good at your job. Isn=E2=80=99t that what you=E2=80=99re supposed to do?=
