<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">AFC Ajax NV suspended its Chief Executive Offi=
cer Alex Kroes and said it plans to dismiss him after =E2=80=9Cstrong indic=
ations=E2=80=9D of insider trading.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The club alleges that Kroes, who was also the =
chairman of Ajax=E2=80=99s executive board, purchased over 17,000 shares of=
 the club a week before his appointment was announced on August 2.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CKroes=E2=80=99 actions are not in lin=
e with what Ajax stands for,=E2=80=9D said Michael van Praag, chairman of t=
he club=E2=80=99s supervisory board, in a statement Tuesday. =E2=80=9CThe t=
iming of his share purchase indicates insider trading. Such a violation of =
the law cannot be tolerated by a publicly listed company, especially when i=
t involves the CEO.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Dutch state broadcaster NOS reported that Kroe=
s did not accept Ajax=E2=80=99s decision to suspend him and will seek an in=
dependent opinion from the market regulator, known as the Dutch Authority f=
or the Financial Markets.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CI believe that you radiate confidence=
 to your fellow shareholders and stakeholders when you buy shares and there=
fore also run financial risks yourself,=E2=80=9D Kroes was cited as saying =
by NOS. =E2=80=9CAs much as I am convinced of my good intentions, I now und=
erstand, after consulting with my lawyer, that I did not make the most sens=
ible decision,=E2=80=9D he said.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Yeah I agree with him? I respect the intention=
s! But it was not all that sensible.</p>
