wed to own companies. Most generally, there is antitrust law: If a company =
in any industry wants to buy another company in that industry, it needs to =
get regulatory approval to make sure the acquisition won=E2=80=99t harm com=
petition. But there are also=C2=A0rules that are specific to individual ind=
ustries. In the US, if you want to own a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
