<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also, in 2014, Jos=C3=A9 Azar, Martin Schmalz =
and Isabel Tecu published a paper on =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.=
bloombergbusiness.com/click/34902854.287353/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYXBlcnMuc3Nybi5jb20=
