th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgrou=
nd-color: #ccc;">Anticompetitive Effects of Common Ownership</a>,=E2=80=9D =
arguing that, when the same investors own a lot of stock in all of the comp=
anies in an industry, that has the effect of pushing up prices for that ind=
ustry=E2=80=99s product. Intuitively, if every airline has different owners=
