order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">implication</a> is that=
=C2=A0<em>antitrust law</em>, which =E2=80=94=C2=A0like every other regulat=
ory regime =E2=80=94=C2=A0tended not to worry about index funds,=C2=A0<em>s=
hould=C2=A0</em>worry about them, because actually their ownership matters =
for antitrust reasons.</p>
